531
00:27:37.823 --> 00:27:39.657
Never tried that before.
I thought it was worth a shot.

532
00:27:39.658 --> 00:27:40.992
- Oh. well.
- That's fucked up!

533
00:27:40.993 --> 00:27:42.535
