539
00:27:50.335 --> 00:27:51.836
at a fucking Norm's!

540
00:27:51.837 --> 00:27:53.796
Sometimes if you lie down.
they don't shoot so much.

541
00:27:53.797 --> 00:27:55.172
You better find
