She's in shock.
Give her the card.

609
00:32:37.789 --> 00:32:40.583
Go tomorrow.
Tonight. just go home.

610
00:32:40.584 --> 00:32:42.126
Why deal with the traffic?

611
00:32:42.127 --> 00:32:44.628
Why deal with it?
Tomorrow's as good as today.

612
00:32:44.629 --> 00:32:46.130
