631
00:34:46.751 --> 00:34:48.335
Glenhurst.

632
00:34:48.336 --> 00:34:49.962
Darren's in the ninth grade.

633
00:34:49.963 --> 00:34:51.630
- He was.
- Ninth grade.

634
00:34:51.631 --> 00:34:53.466
