- Oh. uh...

690
00:37:12.897 --> 00:37:13.857
Weird. I guess.

691
00:37:14.399 --> 00:37:16.234
No. I don't... Um...

692
00:37:17.694 --> 00:37:20.738
Yeah. Yes. weird. He was weird.

693
00:37:21.573 --> 00:37:22.656
