- Mmm.

694
00:37:22.657 --> 00:37:24.575
You know? He was eccentric.

695
00:37:24.576 --> 00:37:26.201
Yeah. sure. sure. sure.

696
00:37:26.202 --> 00:37:29.246
All right. Uh. hobbies!

697
00:37:29.247 --> 00:37:31.540
