773
00:41:46.295 --> 00:41:48.505
Of course you do.

774
00:41:48.506 --> 00:41:50.006
We told you
it would all work out.

775
00:41:50.007 --> 00:41:51.592
Yeah. Yeah.

776
00:41:53.594 --> 00:41:55.303
- I'm just not sure...
- We've all been there.

777
00:41:55.304 --> 00:41:57.931
- Now mingle! Talk to parents.
