798
00:42:49.692 --> 00:42:52.486
- Oh. no.
- Oh. no. No. no. Same kid.

799
00:42:52.487 --> 00:42:54.529
Yeah. four different shootings.

800
00:42:54.530 --> 00:42:56.656
Yeah. we. uh... we lost Claire

801
00:42:56.657 --> 00:42:58.909
two years ago
