855
00:45:15.922 --> 00:45:17.089
- See you. Tom.
- Later.

856
00:45:18.633 --> 00:45:19.842
Here.

857
00:45:21.385 --> 00:45:23.846
Take mine.
I got a bunch of 'em at home.

858
00:45:27.725 --> 00:45:29.477
