Darren. is that you?

866
00:46:05.262 --> 00:46:06.721
Yes. Mom.

867
00:46:06.722 --> 00:46:08.474
You sound tired.

868
00:46:11.811 --> 00:46:14.897
I am tired. baby. I am. It's...

869
00:46:16.107 --> 00:46:18.442
