870
00:46:19.777 --> 00:46:22.195
I miss you. too. So much.

871
00:46:22.196 --> 00:46:24.155
I'm thirsty.

872
00:46:24.156 --> 00:46:26.574
Can you get some
more apple berry peach tea?

873
00:46:26.575 --> 00:46:29.453
It's only got 70 calories per
