- Nobody cares. Nobody cares.

1001
00:52:35.444 --> 00:52:38.071
Just let me see it.
Just for a second. Please.

1002
00:52:38.072 --> 00:52:39.281
- It's an emergency.
- Okay. here.

1003
00:52:40.115 --> 00:52:41.533
What the hell?

1004
00:52:45.662 --> 00:52:47.872
I'm allergic
to cell phones and Wi-Fi.

1005
00:52:47.873 --> 00:52:49.499
You fucking weirdo.

